Sentencas: Polycrystalline samples of La0.6Ca0.4Fe0.8Ni0.2O3 (LCFN) were prepared by the liquid mix process at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of La0.6Ca0.4Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ thin films grown by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The XRD patterns were indexed as the orthoferrite similar to that of PrFeO3 having a single phase orthorhombic perovskite structure (Pbnm).

Sentencas: LCFN films have been deposited on yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) single crystal and polycrystalline substrates at 700 degrees C by pulsed laser deposition (PLD) for application to thin film solid oxide fuel cell cathodes.
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of La0.6Ca0.4Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ thin films grown by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The structure of the films was analyzed by X-ray diffraction (XRD), scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and atomic force microscopy (AFM).
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of La0.6Ca0.4Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ thin films grown by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: Both films are polycrystalline with a marked texture and present pyramidal grains in the surface with different size distribution.
